-------
Display
-------

display: block|inline|inline-block

block: (div, footer, main, hx, p)

inline: (span, em, strong, a, img)

**Width and Height cannot be specified on inline elements**

inline-block: behaves like inline, but (!) we can specify dimensions (Width|Height)

